title: Border Wall Veto, Boeing & 2020 Elections
itunes:title: Border Wall Veto, Boeing & 2020 Elections
description:
Kevin spoke with Jenna Ellis, Trump 2020 campaign advisory board member and constitutional law attorney, and Dave Brown, Democratic Strategist & former advisor to Sen. Patty Murray. They discussed the latest devlopments with Boeing, the tragic shooting in New Zealand, the upcoming elections, and President Trump issuing his first veto, rejecting Congress’s effort to cancel his declaration of a national emergency to pay for a wall on the U.S.-Mexico border.
